{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "仇恕在荒祠中听见沉重脚步，误以为来者不足为惧，却被白袍长发女子慕容惜生拦住。她以毒龙掌和戒杀誓言震慑众人，严厉警告仇恕不得再接近毛文琪。白发道人出面周旋，认出慕容惜生是屠龙仙子首徒，并自报巴山道士柳复明。毛文琪现身阻止师姐破戒，承认仇恕骗她却仍难断情意。慕容惜生带她离去，约仇恕半年后再来。仇恕暗藏杀机又生愧怅。回到正殿后，柳复明向白发老人讲起毛文琪身世、灵蛇毛臬、昆仑一派与毒龙掌旧事。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "枯瘦汉子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "小的一生之中，从来也没有看到比那人再难看的面孔，当时——",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "你是谁？此来何意？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白袍女子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "找你！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "找我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "有何贵干？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白袍女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "白发道人",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "酒未终，筵未散，施主为何就匆匆走了？不该，不该，大是不该。你我萍水相逢，颇觉投缘，且随贫道再去喝两口！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "text": "道长如此抬爱，小可敢不从命？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_niu_san_yan",
      "text": "你这些伴当，此刻穴道解开，血也止住，你替他们上些金创药便可无碍，我且随这道长进去喝两口。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "白发道人",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "这位女施主怎地挡住贫道去路，但请借过一步，让贫道——",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "长发女子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我不管你究竟是什么人，也不管你这样装模作样、鬼鬼祟祟是为了于什么，但是——以后你的手指要是再碰到毛文琪一下，我就斩断你的手指；你的眼睛要是再望毛文琪一眼，我就挖出你的眼睛，而且——现在你要是还不停止你脸上这笑容的话，我就会叫你永远都笑不出来！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "长发女子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "哼",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "阁下说的话，小可一句也听不懂，如果阁下不嫌麻烦的话，就请阁下再说一遍，小可为什么不能看毛姑娘一眼——",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "白发道人",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "贫道虽然置身方外，但让贫道见于绝色美女而不望她两眼，却也无法做到，除非——哈哈，除非这女子的尊容实在不敢领教。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "长发女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "text": "还不走！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "小可正是要走，只是阁下挡住了去路——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "白发道人",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "毒龙掌！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白袍女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "长发女子",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "你看到了吗？这是他逼我动手的，可不是我有心破戒呀！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "师姐，我没有看见！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "文琪，果然是你在这里。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "师姐，我没有看见。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白袍女子",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "我是为你好，你还说没有看见，明明是老道士先向我动手的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "我真的没有看见，何况……何况他也没有先向你动手！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白袍女子",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "你真是没出息，你知不知道人家怎么对你，你这样对他？昨天晚上我跟你说的话，你难道没有听见吗？你说他不会武功，你看他是不是不会武功？他对你到底存着什么坏心思，我虽然不知道，可是——可是——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白袍女子",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "你问问这家伙，他昨天晚上说的什么话，哼！昨天晚上要不是你苦苦拉着我，我才不管什么誓言不誓言，早就跑到你房间隔壁去，把那小子拖出来一刀宰了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白袍女子",
      "listener": "char_ni_lao_qi",
      "text": "你说，你说，你昨天晚上，说的是什么话？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "师姐，我知道你对我好，我也知道他一直在骗我，可是——可是师姐你真的不能和人动手呀，若是被师父知道了——",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白袍女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "text": "你认出了我是谁！可是，你是谁？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "白发道人",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "十七年以前，贫道已忘却姓名，不过——女施主若是坚持要听的话，",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "白发道人",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "贫道就是巴山道士柳复明！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "巴山道人",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "贫道如果老眼不花，那么女施主想必是'屠龙仙子'的首徒——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白袍女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "text": "不错，我就是慕容惜生！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "难怪女施主方才不等贫道出手便不动手，想必是女施主昔年戒杀立誓尚未到期。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "嗯",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "但想来女施主可以再开杀戒之日，已不远了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "text": "正是，等到那一天——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "等到那一天，贫道必定亲至女施主那里引颈待戳，女施主只管放心好了。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "text": "好极。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "阁下要说什么，不必说出小可也知道了，不过，小可要告诉阁下一句，小可与令师妹之间情事，阁下丝毫无权干涉。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "文琪，你说是不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "文琪，我对你怎样，你也该知道，别人的闲话，你为什么要听？为什么要信？难道——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你真的喜欢文琪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "我可怎会骗她！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我把她带回去——",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "你把她带回去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "半年之后，你再来找她，这半年——哼，我会知道你更多些。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "半年，唉——半年已足够了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "半年之后，那慕容惜生戒杀立誓大约已破了，是以她才叫我半年之后去找她们，那时她就不必像今天一样有这多顾忌。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_san_yan",
      "speaker_name": "牛三眼",
      "listener": "char_ni_lao_qi",
      "text": "这小娘儿们，真有点邪气。喂，倪老七，你怎地这么脓包，在娘儿们面前穷吼些什么，真是丢公子的人，哼，也丢了我'牛三眼'的人，大胡子，快去把倪老七扶回来！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "怎地去了这么久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "text": "方才我在外面遇着一人，你且猜上一猜，此人是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "text": "茫茫众生，我认得几人？我一人也不认得，你教我如何猜法。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "text": "此人你我虽俱不认得，却是你我一个故人之女，哈哈——此人就是那灵蛇毛臬的女儿，她虽没有说出，但我却已猜到！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "text": "毛臬是谁？唉——往事已矣，毛臬我也不再认得了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "text": "你可知道我们这故人之女已拜在何人门下？她竟又拜在那'屠龙仙子'的门下，你可记得你我在昆仑山下听到的那段故事，哈哈——我今日竟遇着了那慕容惜生，还和她对了两掌，她果然不敢破那戒杀十年之戒，看来昆仑一派，近年来虽已无昔日之盛，但却仍未可轻视呢！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "text": "火将熄，肉将冷，你还是快些吃罢……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "text": "这'屠龙仙子'究竟是谁？道长在昆仑山下听到的又是何事？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "说起那'屠龙仙子'，倒的确是位女中奇人，数十年前，她本是个独行女盗，武功绝高，但却嗜杀，黑白两道，无论是谁，只要撞在她手里，被她轻轻拍上一掌，立时便是骨化魂飞之祸，竟无一人能逃得活命的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "是了，百十年来，武林中若论拳法之奇，当然是那纵横天下的前辈异人'海天孤燕'所使的'化骨神拳'，若论掌法之毒，却就得数这'毒龙掌'了，这'毒龙掌'之毒，在别人看来，掌风软弱，似是毫不起眼，但只要沾着一些，便无药可救。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "是以方才你若硬接了慕容惜生那一掌，那么——唉，你武功虽高，但你手掌只要被她的手掌伤着少许，大约也无法幸免。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "当时武林中人伤在她这'毒龙掌'下的，不知凡几，那时武林中人却叫她做'毒龙魔女'，将她恨之切骨，却无可奈何，直到一天，她突地扬言天下，此后绝不再用'毒龙掌'，自此以后，她也真的谨守诺言，不但不再施那'毒龙掌法'，而且未再伤过一人之命，于是武林中为祸最烈的一条'毒龙'，从此除去，而她的名字也由'毒龙魔女'变为'屠龙仙子'了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "柳复明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昔日周处勇除三害，传为千古美谈，这“屠龙仙子”的行径，也正和他相差无几。哈哈——毒龙自屠，毒龙屠龙，这“屠龙仙子”的名字，委实用得妙极！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 348
    }
  ],
